Ahead of the Homecoming Pop-up opening Friday in Lagos, the annual festival reveals its 2019 Fashion Editorial shot by Nigerian photographers Stephen Tayo and Danielle Mbonu. Photographed on the streets of Lagos, the editorial centres include fashion labels such as Alyx, Nike, Ambush and a host of others The editorial showcases exclusive designs created by each brand for the festival, which will retail at the XII Glover, Lagos, between April 19 and 21. Featured within the offering are a slew of limited edition designs from international and local brands, including original collaborations between Awake NY x Motherlan, and Nike x Homecoming. Designs pay tribute to the spirit of Nigeria and its creative culture, and to Homecoming as a celebration of cultural exchange and collaboration.